name: 1.0.0a4
body:
### This release is Alpha.
**Use is encouraged for testing and feedback is appreciated, but it is not recommended to use the 1.0.0 series in production yet.**

- From scratch rewrite providing a consistent CLI experience and a vast array of new and advanced features. Please see the [1.0.0 Milestone](https://github.com/Azure/blobxfer/milestone/1) for a catalog of changes.
- **Breaking Changes:** there have been a significant number of breaking changes with the rewrite from the command-line invocation of `blobxfer` itself to the options and environment variable names. Please review [the usage documentation](https://github.com/Azure/blobxfer/blob/develop/docs) carefully when upgrading from 0.12.1.

For a full list of changes, please see the [Change Log](https://github.com/Azure/blobxfer/blob/develop/CHANGELOG.md).

This release targets the [1.0.0 Milestone](https://github.com/Azure/blobxfer/milestone/1).
Please see the [Change Log](https://github.com/Azure/blobxfer/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md) for changes.

name: 0.12.0 Release
body:
#### Added
- Support for Account-level SAS keys
- Update README regarding non-normalized exceptions being thrown (#5)

name: 0.11.5 Release
body:
#### Changed
- Update all dependencies to latest versions

#### Fixed
- Fix incorrect fileshare path splitting (#3)

#### Security
- Update cryptography requirement to 1.5.2
